## ðŸ”„ Pattern Variations & Combinations

### Common Combinations
- **With [[Kidney Yang Deficiency]]:** This is the root pattern, and they are almost always diagnosed together. The treatment for Bladder Deficient and Cold is inherently a treatment for Kidney Yang Deficiency.
- **With [[Spleen Qi Sinking]]:** If there is also a bearing-down sensation, prolapse, or severe fatigue, Spleen Qi Deficiency is also involved. Combine with herbs and points to tonify and lift Spleen Qi, such as [[Huang Qi]] and [[ST-36 (Zu San Li)]].

